* '''{{ill|Kushiyama Kofun|ja|櫛山古墳|12=draft|12=draft}}''' ({{ill|Tenri, Nara|ja|天理市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ウィキ座標|34|33|24.68|N|135|51|7.54|E|region:JP-29_type:landmark|name=Kushiyama Kofun}})
* '''Three tombs in the {{ill|Iwaseoyama Kofun Cluster|ja|石清尾山古墳群|1=Iwaseoyama Kofun Cluster|12=draft|12=draft}}''' ({{ill|Takamatsu, Kagawa|ja|高松市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kagawa Prefecture|ja|香川県|12=draft|12=draft}}):
** '''{{ill|Nekozuka Kofun|ja|猫塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}}''' ({{Coord|34|19|39.63|N|134|1|25.08|E|region:JP-37_type:landmark|name=Nekozuka Kofun}}) * '''Pile-stone tomb (積石塚)'''.
