* '''Three tombs in the [[:en:Iwaseoyama Kofun Cluster|Iwaseoyama Kofun Cluster]]''' ([[:en:Takamatsu|Takamatsu, Kagawa]], [[:en:Kagawa Prefecture|Kagawa Prefecture]]):
